metadata.name: THE EXPEDITION
metadata.description:
"We can only imagine the secrets it holds and the wonders it will reveal. This discovery will change the course of history, and we are honored to be the ones to bring it to light. No one believed it could actually exist. Until we found it."

Size: 4200px x 5250px
Format: PNG
Software used: AI, Adobe Photoshop, Procreate

"ALTERNATE REALITIES" collection is the result of the collaboration between human creativity and artificial intelligence, fusing the newest and older digital tools to explore different sci-fi and retro cyberpunk concepts. The classical painterly style, blended with futuristic themes, is meant to create a timeless aesthetic that transcends the trends of the moment. It's a reminder that art is not just a product of its time, but also a combination of influences, a reflection of the interaction between human imagination and ever-evolving creative tools.
